title: Lifehouse
text:
'''Lifehouse''' may refer to:

==Churches ==
* [[Lifehouse International Church]], a network of churches in Asia 
* [[CRC Churches International#Locations |Lifehouse]], a CRC International church in Murray Bridge, South Australia 

==Music==
* [[Lifehouse (band)]], an American rock band
** [[Lifehouse (album)|''Lifehouse'' (album)]] (2005), the band's self-titled album
* [[Lifehouse (rock opera)|''Lifehouse'' (rock opera)]], a rock opera by the British rock band The Who

==Other uses==
* [[Lifehouse (novel)|''Lifehouse'' (novel)]] (1982), a science-fiction novel by Spider Robinson
